p.k: The Watterson kids come up with a fool-proof plan. / Gumball accidentally uploads a video of himself and wants it gone. / Gumball and Darwin's reputation is challenged and they really couldn't care less... / Gumball and Darwin fail to make some instant homemade movie classics. / Richard is left in charge for the day, but his lack of rules attracts unwanted guests to the Watterson house. / Gumball and Darwin try to understand Juke's urgent beatbox message. / Gumball and Darwin must apologise to everyone they know after getting a threatening message on Elmore Plus. / Darwin has promised to play video games with Gumball, but his promise with Banana Joe interferes. / The Wattersons must survive a bizarre game of Dodj or Daar through to the end.
